author: donaldp
msg: Make changes so that tasks use the two arg replaceProperties() rather than 3 arg as it is lower coupling.

author: donaldp
msg: Add a method replaceProperties(Project,String). This delegates directly to replaceProperties(Project,String,HashMap). The Map parameter contains all the properties in Project.
This makes it easier to have a lighter coupling between tasks and Project.

author: donaldp
msg: Remove unsetProperty() because it allows tasks to break immutability.
